68
00:03:57,473 --> 00:03:59,193
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though that was her decision,</b></font>

69
00:03:59,913 --> 00:04:01,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I went there and left.</b></font>

70
00:04:02,113 --> 00:04:04,473
