84
00:04:43,873 --> 00:04:44,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you regret it?</b></font>

85
00:04:48,593 --> 00:04:49,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I do.</b></font>

86
00:04:51,353 --> 00:04:54,233
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I regret giving up on her so easily.</b></font>

87
00:04:55,753 --> 00:04:58,433
