<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I want to hold on to my happiness now.</i></b></font>

381
00:31:15,153 --> 00:31:16,113
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you hungry?</b></font>

382
00:31:17,593 --> 00:31:18,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It wasn't me.</b></font>

383
00:31:18,713 --> 00:31:19,953
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It wasn't me.</b></font>

384
00:31:20,073 --> 00:31:21,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm sure it was you. I heard it.</b></font>

385
00:31:21,793 --> 00:31:23,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The sound came from your stomach!</b></font>

386
00:31:23,593 --> 00:31:25,793
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Why are you accusing me?
-Just because...</b></font>

387
00:31:27,993 --> 00:31:30,953
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Since you looked so cute
when you accused me,</b></font>

388
00:31:31,033 --> 00:31:34,313
<font color="#ffff00"><b>a chivalrous person like me
won't argue with you anymore.</b></font>

389
00:31:34,793 --> 00:31:36,673
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When did I accuse you?</b></font>

390
00:31:36,753 --> 00:31:38,233
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Let's eat.</b></font>

391
00:31:46,233 --> 00:31:47,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you holding my hand so tightly?</b></font>

392
00:31:49,633 --> 00:31:51,113
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm afraid you'll run away.</b></font>

393
00:31:51,353 --> 00:31:52,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm thinking</b></font>

394
00:31:52,913 --> 00:31:55,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I should have borrowed handcuffs
from that officer earlier.</b></font>

395
00:31:55,913 --> 00:31:57,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then you won't be able to run away.</b></font>

396
00:31:58,713 --> 00:31:59,633
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Silly boy.</b></font>

397
00:32:00,593 --> 00:32:01,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's go eat ramen.</b></font>

398
00:32:02,553 --> 00:32:03,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ramen?</b></font>

399
00:32:03,793 --> 00:32:05,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why should we eat ramen?</b></font>

400
00:32:05,193 --> 00:32:06,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you thinking?</b></font>

401
00:32:06,633 --> 00:32:07,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm thinking of eating ramen.</b></font>

402
00:32:08,753 --> 00:32:09,953
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then what are you thinking?</b></font>

403
00:32:12,033 --> 00:32:14,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It suddenly feels like we're flirting.</i></b></font>

404
00:32:14,793 --> 00:32:16,633
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>What should I do to break the awkwardness?</i></b></font>

405
00:32:19,553 --> 00:32:20,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know.</b></font>

406
00:32:22,073 --> 00:32:23,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're thinking about me, right?</b></font>

407
00:32:26,793 --> 00:32:27,873
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop being so narcissistic.</b></font>

408
00:32:30,393 --> 00:32:32,793
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Goodness.</i> <i>What did I just say?</i></b></font>

409
00:32:32,993 --> 00:32:34,713
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It's even more awkward now.</i></b></font>

410
00:32:39,073 --> 00:32:40,393
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's so funny.</b></font>

411
00:32:42,313 --> 00:32:43,273
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How is that funny?</b></font>

412
00:32:43,433 --> 00:32:44,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are we eating or not?</b></font>

413
00:32:45,233 --> 00:32:46,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Wasn't it funny?
-Not at all.</b></font>

414
00:32:47,233 --> 00:32:48,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Okay.
-It was not funny.</b></font>

415
00:32:53,913 --> 00:32:54,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey!</b></font>

416
00:33:28,433 --> 00:33:30,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sir, can you please stop the bus?</b></font>

417
00:33:31,513 --> 00:33:33,353
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm begging you! It's very important.</b></font>

418
00:33:42,593 --> 00:33:43,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

419
00:33:44,833 --> 00:33:45,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you sure?</b></font>

420
00:33:47,993 --> 00:33:50,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei, I want to give it a try.</b></font>

421
00:33:50,873 --> 00:33:52,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Compared to trying my best and failing,</b></font>

422
00:33:53,393 --> 00:33:55,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>not trying at all would make me
regret it even more.</b></font>

423
00:34:35,633 --> 00:34:36,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Excuse me.</b></font>

424
00:34:37,953 --> 00:34:39,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is your ramen. Please enjoy.</b></font>

425
00:34:41,553 --> 00:34:42,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It looks so good.</b></font>

426
00:34:44,713 --> 00:34:46,033
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Okay, thanks.
-You're welcome.</b></font>

427
00:34:56,473 --> 00:34:57,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why aren't you eating?</b></font>

428
00:34:58,993 --> 00:35:00,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm suddenly not that hungry.</b></font>

429
00:35:01,153 --> 00:35:02,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's such a waste not to eat it.</b></font>

430
00:35:03,113 --> 00:35:04,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay, fine.</b></font>

431
00:35:14,713 --> 00:35:16,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How is it? Is it good?</b></font>

432
00:35:17,033 --> 00:35:18,193
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, it's all right.</b></font>

433
00:35:24,753 --> 00:35:25,633
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

434
00:35:26,513 --> 00:35:27,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you have a passport?</b></font>

435
00:35:28,273 --> 00:35:29,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes, I do.</b></font>

436
00:35:30,033 --> 00:35:32,033
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I applied for one
the last time I went overseas.</b></font>

437
00:35:32,553 --> 00:35:33,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then there's no problem.</b></font>

438
00:35:34,353 --> 00:35:35,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

439
00:35:38,713 --> 00:35:40,673
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, let's go to London together.</b></font>

440
00:35:45,913 --> 00:35:46,873
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You mean...</b></font>

441
00:35:49,433 --> 00:35:51,793
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that newly-opened London coffee shop?</b></font>

442
00:35:52,953 --> 00:35:55,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think we need to come up
with a plan soon.</b></font>

443
00:35:55,593 --> 00:35:56,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My mom is not that easy to handle.</b></font>

444
00:36:00,513 --> 00:36:01,353
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wait.</b></font>

445
00:36:02,313 --> 00:36:03,873
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't we being too rash?</b></font>

446
00:36:03,953 --> 00:36:04,953
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you want to?</b></font>

447
00:36:09,073 --> 00:36:09,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

448
00:36:10,153 --> 00:36:11,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't.</b></font>

449
00:36:11,553 --> 00:36:12,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

450
00:36:13,353 --> 00:36:14,513
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

451
00:36:16,113 --> 00:36:18,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to go to a foreign country.</b></font>

452
00:36:19,713 --> 00:36:21,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't have friends there</b></font>

453
00:36:23,033 --> 00:36:26,313
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and my English is bad.
I'm not used to Western food.</b></font>

454
00:36:27,353 --> 00:36:29,113
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What if I get sick?</b></font>

455
00:36:32,633 --> 00:36:34,273
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then why did you get off the bus?</b></font>

456
00:36:43,553 --> 00:36:44,713
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did I misunderstand?</b></font>

457
00:36:46,273 --> 00:36:47,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why did you get off the bus?</b></font>

458
00:36:49,153 --> 00:36:50,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Is this guy</i></b></font>

459
00:36:51,033 --> 00:36:52,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>pushing me to make things clear?</i></b></font>

460
00:36:55,313 --> 00:36:56,873
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can't I get off the bus?</b></font>

461
00:37:02,153 --> 00:37:03,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I see.</b></font>

462
00:37:05,393 --> 00:37:06,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll go ahead.</b></font>

463
00:37:12,873 --> 00:37:14,753
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>What exactly am I saying?</i></b></font>

464
00:37:20,633 --> 00:37:21,633
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si, wait!</b></font>

465
00:37:34,233 --> 00:37:35,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

466
00:37:44,033 --> 00:37:45,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to say...</b></font>

467
00:37:57,673 --> 00:37:58,873
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Good night.</b></font>

468
00:38:02,953 --> 00:38:03,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's it?</b></font>

469
00:38:06,153 --> 00:38:07,273
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's it.</b></font>

470
00:39:03,113 --> 00:39:04,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you looking for me?</b></font>

471
00:39:06,313 --> 00:39:09,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I just want to tell you in person
that Shancai is mine.</b></font>

472
00:39:09,673 --> 00:39:10,713
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't bother her anymore.</b></font>

473
00:39:12,273 --> 00:39:13,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So you're together now?</b></font>

474
00:39:14,193 --> 00:39:15,433
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is Shancai your girlfriend?</b></font>

475
00:39:15,913 --> 00:39:17,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's none of your business!</b></font>

476
00:39:22,953 --> 00:39:23,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't think she is.</b></font>

477
00:39:26,993 --> 00:39:28,393
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I still have a chance then.</b></font>

478
00:39:33,233 --> 00:39:35,833
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you get it?
Tell me that you're giving up on Shancai.</b></font>

479
00:39:37,833 --> 00:39:39,673
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't see why I should do that.</b></font>

480
00:39:41,633 --> 00:39:42,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei.</b></font>

481
00:39:43,153 --> 00:39:44,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Am I not your friend anymore?</b></font>

482
00:39:44,953 --> 00:39:46,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You know I can't live without Shancai.</b></font>

483
00:39:46,673 --> 00:39:47,633
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You know I--
-I don't.</b></font>

484
00:39:47,713 --> 00:39:48,553
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You...</b></font>

485
00:39:48,633 --> 00:39:50,593
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know you hurt her with your temper.</b></font>

486
00:39:50,673 --> 00:39:52,193
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How could I hurt her?</b></font>

487
00:39:52,433 --> 00:39:54,473
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Give up on Shancai, understand?</b></font>

488
00:39:56,673 --> 00:39:58,953
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not deaf. You don't have to shout.</b></font>

489
00:40:05,553 --> 00:40:06,713
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't care what you think.</b></font>

490
00:40:06,793 --> 00:40:08,913
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm warning you.</b></font>

491
00:40:08,993 --> 00:40:10,273
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai is mine.</b></font>

492
00:40:10,473 --> 00:40:12,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I, Daoming Si, will be
responsible for her.</b></font>

493
00:40:12,233 --> 00:40:13,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll take care of her.</b></font>

494
00:40:14,353 --> 00:40:17,993
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't let her be with a guy like you.
A guy who has no conscience and loyalty.</b></font>

495
00:40:18,953 --> 00:40:20,193
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you hear that?</b></font>

496
00:40:29,713 --> 00:40:31,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Oh, all right.</b></font>

497
00:40:31,233 --> 00:40:33,153
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean, "Oh, all right"?
What exactly...</b></font>

498
00:40:39,113 --> 00:40:40,073
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What did you say again?</b></font>

499
00:40:40,873 --> 00:40:41,793
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I said all right.</b></font>

500
00:40:42,153 --> 00:40:43,113
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll give up on Shancai.</b></font>

501
00:40:45,353 --> 00:40:46,233
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

502
00:40:48,233 --> 00:40:50,713
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-So I can pursue Shancai?
-No.</b></font>

